    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 和 Salesforce 签署承诺，打造人工智能造福人类</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/openai-salesforce-sign-pledge-to-build-ai-for-good-of-humanity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI、Salesforce Inc. 和其他科技公司签署了一封公开信，强调了“最大限度地发挥人工智能的好处并减轻社会风险”的“集体责任”，这是科技行业呼吁负责任地构建人工智能的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/openai-salesforce-sign-pledge-to-build-ai-for-good-of-humanity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citizens首席执行官Van Saun：人工智能是市场的首要考虑因素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-04/citizens-ceo-van-saun-ai-is-top-of-mind-for-the-market-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公民金融集团董事长兼首席执行官 Bruce Van Saun 与 Ed Ludlow 和 Caroline Hyde 一起讨论了该公司如何将人工智能融入其运营、Reddit IPO 以及一年前硅谷银行倒闭的教训。他在“彭博科技”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-04/citizens-ceo-van-saun-ai-is-top-of-mind-for-the-market-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:03:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊带领企业投资 100 亿美元建设沙特数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/amazon-leads-firms-investing-10-billion-in-saudi-data-centers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯表示，随着这个沙漠王国试图实现其依赖石油的经济现代化和多元化，包括亚马逊网络服务在内的公司将投资超过 100 亿美元在该国建设数据中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/amazon-leads-firms-investing-10-billion-in-saudi-data-centers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:11:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果为 MacBook Air 添加 M3 芯片 老款降价 100 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/apple-adds-m3-chip-to-macbook-air-old-model-gets-100-price-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司周一更新了 13 英寸和 15 英寸 MacBook Air 型号，增加了速度稍快的 M3 处理器，并降低了之前版本的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/apple-adds-m3-chip-to-macbook-air-old-model-gets-100-price-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:19:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉提议为巴西优步司机提供更强有力的劳动保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/brazil-s-lula-to-propose-stronger-labor-protections-for-uber-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦正在推动加强优步科技公司和类似客运应用程序司机的劳工权利，应对困扰世界各地立法者的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/brazil-s-lula-to-propose-stronger-labor-protections-for-uber-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 15:07:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大宗商品贸易商托克将通过 Greenergy 交易种植生物柴油，为零售业提供燃料</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/trafigura-agrees-to-buy-greenergy-s-european-biofuels-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大宗商品贸易公司托克集团同意从布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司收购生物柴油生产商和燃料供应商 Greenergy 的欧洲业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/trafigura-agrees-to-buy-greenergy-s-european-biofuels-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 14:44:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩表示，如果董事会被罢免，将考虑对 SoftwareOne 进行新的收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/bain-said-to-mull-fresh-bid-for-softwareone-if-board-is-ousted</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，如果瑞士 SoftwareOne Holding AG 的创始股东下个月成功罢免董事会，贝恩资本有兴趣再次尝试收购这家公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/bain-said-to-mull-fresh-bid-for-softwareone-if-board-is-ousted</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:25:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果因音乐应用程序滥用而被欧盟罚款 18 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/apple-hit-with-1-8-billion-eu-fine-over-abusive-app-store-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司周一因涉嫌在其平台上拒绝包括 Spotify Technology SA 在内的音乐流媒体竞争对手的指控而受到欧盟 18 亿欧元（合 20 亿美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/apple-hit-with-1-8-billion-eu-fine-over-abusive-app-store-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:01:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于专注于营销支出，Sea Share放弃了涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/sea-earnings-fall-less-than-expected-on-solid-e-commerce-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sea Ltd.回吐了早些时候的大部分涨幅，因为投资者消化了一份总体积极的收益报告，该报告显示了营销方面的积极支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/sea-earnings-fall-less-than-expected-on-solid-e-commerce-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:42:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达超越阿美公司，成为全球第三大最有价值公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/nvidia-leaps-aramco-to-be-world-s-third-most-valuable-company</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的市值超越沙特阿美公司 (Saudi Aramco)，成为继苹果公司 (Apple Inc.) 和微软公司 (Microsoft Corp.) 之后全球第三大最有价值的上市公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/nvidia-leaps-aramco-to-be-world-s-third-most-valuable-company</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
